{"tid":877782,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救][有圖]電腦顯示有問題","createTime":"2018-10-26T15:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T18:27:48.000Z","uid":16306,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ea88fee19845a2f3ecfdf794ab73f3c98ed0b3da","tid":877782,"uid":16306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T15:22:29.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟部電腦幾星期前開始有呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係長時間待完機再wake up嘅時候<br />\n成個mon啲嘢會濛曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/26/230559_209669c64826c7881210763d096f7e67.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2F230559_209669c64826c7881210763d096f7e67.png&h=516ee8f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正常係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/26/231227_ce2be6785f6d6e46bb47b9de00a5d4cd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2F231227_ce2be6785f6d6e46bb47b9de00a5d4cd.png&h=e8af6d5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而cap圖係會cap到正常畫面<br />\n暫時唯一解決方法係喺windows setting 入面轉另一個resolution 再轉返正常嘅resolution <br />\n不過喺未轉之前windows 同nvidia 都顯示我係run緊正常resolution <br />\n同埋佢一轉另一個resolution 嗰時成個mon都會black out 成兩分鐘左右先轉到（平時正常1、2秒就ok)<br />\n已經試過update 同重裝display driver<br />\n都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGoogle過又冇類似問題<br />\n有冇巴打知點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb674ae42b575243f13eca996bc0283a8ce7167a","tid":877782,"uid":26429,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T15:24:36.000Z","msg":"我可能打得飛機太多<br />\n我睇唔出有咩分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f8202b0c22b8bcf47f521f408ab8496e214bc6","tid":877782,"uid":16306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T15:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cec43569ab6c8d28f12faaed723ec3d3cc59305","tid":877782,"uid":16306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:52:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/004913_deced0db13da844b56cae9780a385f49.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F004913_deced0db13da844b56cae9780a385f49.png&h=af6fd048&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/004915_1768848eb51e23994a3a517041c588c7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F004915_1768848eb51e23994a3a517041c588c7.png&h=10326615&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頭先發現轉refresh rate都可以<br />\n不過又係要等好耐先有返signal 去個mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a139d3750d095081210173916542315b3ff0f8a","tid":877782,"uid":187316,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:59:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4cebfb7fa5e18bf2c138b58266da6da85fb2371","tid":877782,"uid":16306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T17:02:42.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec80fc9098dc2b6f46fe8acd707048efdec8084d","tid":877782,"uid":40052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T17:05:52.000Z","msg":"隻Mon setting?"},{"pid":"8c57843e4fc8dbbb8438ee07c67c47427f070af8","tid":877782,"uid":16306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s